%e A215494 We have a(3)=5*7^2 and a(6)=5*7^4, which implies that s(1)^12 + s(2)^12 + s(4)^12 = 49*(s(1)^6 + s(2)^6 + s(4)^6). We also have a(9) = (a(1) + a(3))*7^49.
